{"tid":527782,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"咖啡不是用來提神，是用來享受 ，對不對？","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T17:50:14.000Z","uid":123335,"like":62,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5d371dbe4dda2be8ba39f20d2a0a3bab407ade5b","tid":527782,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:07:19.000Z","msg":"靠咖啡因提神<br />\n抗藥性好快出現<br />\n連續飲3日, 提神作用顯著大減<br />\n咖啡提神 ?  錯了，錯了 <br />\n<br />\n其實<br />\n咖啡真正既作用, 係源自 : <br />\n<br />\n果種香氣, 果種濃烈<br />\n強烈衝擊大家既嗅覺神經<br />\n真係索一索, 舒筋活絡<br />\n<br />\n直接一淡飲落口<br />\n果種酸酸苦澀既味道<br />\n簡直同人生一鳩樣<br />\n路是苦，仍要走<br />\n啡是苦，仍要飲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加入牛奶後果種口感<br />\n温柔敦厚，內涵層次感豐富 <br />\n一白一黑，混埋一起中和<br />\n完全體現到咩叫中庸之道，平衡既大智慧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主我嘆每一杯咖啡<br />\n都嚐到人生崎嶇 , 路仍必須走既人生哲理 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160664ddbb5cd9914bff85794a293de4a5c5c514","tid":527782,"uid":47674,"like":86,"dislike":6,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"飲杯咖啡都咁撚作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f96e514c2d1d1a25d1d81bf487947906f5f66f7","tid":527782,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"@深夜小狗"},{"pid":"5fc743ca1cb150780cb37ebff0cbf4bb629553b3","tid":527782,"uid":81150,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"我夠知人要有既係生活  並唔係生存啦<br />\n<br />\n琴晚ot到十二點呀   享受個撚咩"},{"pid":"d1d227b12adf66b1bc91c27616b880c720a29074","tid":527782,"uid":28214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"加豆奶先正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ec81d03b5ff3bc13cc89b14c8f9387953b1540","tid":527782,"uid":87389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:48:30.000Z","msg":"人奶latte<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83282d143af6dd3163f53c50f658744b3bbd4a91","tid":527782,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"加奶好難飲"},{"pid":"6a421750ae4af9b9cb9784e297fe63ca6442c4b4","tid":527782,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"a70cdcec498ff5bb3232594c39bbe8028a3f0e20","tid":527782,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"Why not both <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2d99413c740c512bdbbbaef44b0d5553a41e9b","tid":527782,"uid":63432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"講真 呢d級數既咖啡你地唔會飲到"},{"pid":"c69ab96f6437e58ced4341e9410754360dc8543f","tid":527782,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"講乜撚野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d103f514f2d2187e24be728debf5e32386508e","tid":527782,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2d99413c740c512bdbbbaef44b0d5553a41e9b","tid":527782,"uid":63432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"講真 呢d級數既咖啡你地唔會飲到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.youarebeautiful.jp/asset/2016/05/IMG_2480-e1462625494859-560x560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youarebeautiful.jp%2Fasset%2F2016%2F05%2FIMG_2480-e1462625494859-560x560.jpg&h=1d1346dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4659846cbe9f5ff95ed564235b6625187688c95c","tid":527782,"uid":151773,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"商品咖啡用黎提神 (大部份用R)<br />\n精品咖啡似茶似酒 有好多唔同風味<br />\n配合唔同器材 唔同玩法 <br />\n<br />\n羅拔斯塔種Robusta嘅咖啡因<br />\n比阿拉比卡種Arabica高1倍<br />\n<br />\nR用黎做罐裝&amp;即溶就正<br />\n因為啱晒香港人想提神，要快，要簡單嘅宗旨<br />\n科學上解釋 飲左咖啡因 會令大腦暫停吸收腺苷 腺苷會令人疲累 (咖啡因同腺苷好相似，咖啡因頂住個腦，腺苷就入唔到去)<br />\n 另外 咖啡因都會促進賢上腺素產生<br />\n<br />\nbut高分嘅R 係好飲過 低分嘅A<br />\n香港人飲得起嘅<br />\n自己買靚豆返屋企飲係好過出面連鎖店買杯曳嘅啡飲"},{"pid":"739a9bfd1ba0331e1acd5a7d85b0c74df93481d8","tid":527782,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:10:24.000Z","msg":"Royal級咖啡"},{"pid":"721d82056b47ef4fb97f2ac06015fcf9ac0a9222","tid":527782,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"我試過有次用咖啡浣腸"},{"pid":"2ce0036d4ff81929cfc3470c2cfb305380aa9e3c","tid":527782,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f96e514c2d1d1a25d1d81bf487947906f5f66f7","tid":527782,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"@深夜小狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e132b741a35cc8b2bb25e03cec819a577cf58acf","tid":527782,"uid":41315,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2d99413c740c512bdbbbaef44b0d5553a41e9b","tid":527782,"uid":63432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"講真 呢d級數既咖啡你地唔會飲到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n香港都有好多出色既 精品咖啡店<br />\n真係有, 唔少的<br />\n<br />\n不過香港咖啡文化低落<br />\n新假期又唔會報道佢<br />\n就無香港人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得自己個圈子既人知道"},{"pid":"3940fd1b13f2f080ef3dc0b41e51ad8f51876e36","tid":527782,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e132b741a35cc8b2bb25e03cec819a577cf58acf","tid":527782,"uid":41315,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2d99413c740c512bdbbbaef44b0d5553a41e9b","tid":527782,"uid":63432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"講真 呢d級數既咖啡你地唔會飲到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n香港都有好多出色既 精品咖啡店<br />\n真係有, 唔少的<br />\n<br />\n不過香港咖啡文化低